title: All Champion Team Skins are missing!
body: I was looking through my champions and their skins because over the years I've gotten all the legacy skins, and alot of the really cool looking skins, and I just wanted to see the art for Tpa Shen again, with those noise makers for his weapons, but the skin was not on my list, All the Tpa, Fnatic, and SKT T1 skins are all missing, am I the only one missing these?

replies.body: Just to confirm with what *Iron Chimera* mentioned, are you able to select them in champion select but not see them listed on your profile? Your initial post didn't clear this up, so I just want to ensure I understand the issue.
OH WOW SORRY! I didn't notice this response! After the TPA skins and such returned to the shop, they showed up on my list in champion select, but before, no they were not! :)

I went ahead and checked in a custom and the skin was still there to be selected among my skins, but it wasn't in the viewing portion of the skins outside of it.  I'm not sure what to make of it, but maybe we will get an explanation at some point?
I went to go look i have no skt t1 vayne anymore :(
